The global pallet displays market can be segmented based on material type, product type, application, and distribution channel. In terms of material type, the market includes segments such as corrugated board, foam board, plastic sheet, metal, and others. The product type segment comprises full pallet display, half pallet display, quarter pallet display, and customized pallet display. On the basis of application, the market is categorized into food & beverages, cosmetics & personal care, pharmaceuticals, electronics, retail stores, and others. Concerning distribution channels, the market covers hypermarkets & supermarkets, convenience stores, specialty stores, and online retail.

